{"tid":1661736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有美國國會議員出手叫奧委會唔好畀北京主辦冬奧！","createTime":"2019-10-18T09:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T10:21:50.000Z","uid":263189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4390d7943ac65bc805f6830f7af7a8e3af37a135","tid":1661736,"uid":263189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"【Senator Rick Scott去信奧委會主席籲重新審視北京冬奧主辦權😼】<br />\n<br />\n//在信中，斯科特向國際奧委會主席巴赫（Thomas Bach）表示，近日曾赴港觀察，並與不少正在爭取基本自由的勇敢港人見面，他指中共已將香港變成「警察城市」，強迫市民去遵從北京的旨意。如中共繼續打破承諾、違反人權，打壓香港人，就不應讓北京主辦 2022 年冬季奧運會。他指國際奧委會要面對一個「重要的決定」，奧運會是讓全球最好的運動員，代表自己的國家競技，「奧運會不應由對人權缺乏尊重的中共和習近平主辦」，他促請奧委會為捍衛自由發聲，並要求中共做「正確的事」，否則就為 2022 年冬奧另找主辦國 。//<br />\n<br />\n📨Full Letter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rickscott.senate.gov/sites/default/files/2019-10/191017-Thomas%20Bach%20IOC.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rickscott.senate.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2019-10%2F191017-Thomas%2520Bach%2520IOC.pdf&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizxQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=e1b63d7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rickscott.senate.gov/sites/default/files/2019-10/191017-Thomas%20Bach%20IOC.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%A5%A7%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E7%B1%B2%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%AF%A9%E8%A6%96%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC-2022-%E5%86%AC%E5%A5%A7%E4%B8%BB%E8%BE%A6%E6%AC%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC-2022-%25E5%2586%25AC%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25AC%258A%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizxQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=efd0f312\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%